title: I Was Summoned to Be a Miko, but the Guy with Me was So High-Spec that They Didn’t Need Me - Novel Updates
tags: Adventurers   Average-looking Protagonist   Betrayal   Bisexual Protagonist   Calm Protagonist   Fantasy World   Late Romance   Low-key Protagonist   Magic   Manly Gay Couple   Naive Protagonist   Royalty   Transported to Another World   Weak to Strong
author: 新藤皐月
description:
On the way home from work, I was summoned to another world to be a Miko, along with a young man I just met.

He had good, strong abilities, perfect for the role of Miko, and thus had to carry the expectations of the world alone.

I, meanwhile, with my lesser abilities, had to somehow survive in a foreign world after leaving everything I knew behind. >
